Haɗuwa mai saurin ƙaruwa na cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020
Cigaban kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya wanda ya tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa matakin ya bambanta daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, cutar ta COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Dangane da kwarewar Italiya, ya kamata jihohi, asibitoci, da rukunin kula da gaggawa su inganta shirye-shiryensu don karuwar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 waɗanda zasu buƙaci kulawa ta kiwon lafiya, musamman kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu rahoton wani gungu na masu kamuwa da cutar huhu da ba a san asalin su ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, na kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa, kwayar cutar coronavirus ce da ake kira SARS-CoV-2.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaida ta nuna cewa kusan kashi 80 cikin 100 na waɗanda ke fama da COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtukan numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma mafi yawan waɗannan marasa lafiya sun warke.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin ɗari na cutar, COVID-19 ta zama mafi tsanani kuma tana buƙatar kulawar asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin ɗari na sauran cutar ta zama mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin dari.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika yanayin tarin cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da United Kingdom sannan muka kwatanta shi da wanda ya faru a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya da adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Al'amuran COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya sami ƙarin yaduwar ƙasa kuma yanayin annobar COVID-19 a sauran sassan duniya yanzu yana bin yanayin annobar a China.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon Turai tare da tabbatar da shari'ar COVID-19 bisa ga ma'anar yanayin WHO.
A EU/EEA, Faransa ta fara ba da rahoton mutane uku da suka kamu da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, na kasar Sin.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da Ingila (UK), tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da 15 ga Maris, 2020 tare da waɗannan kwanakin, an sami shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 da aka ruwaito, tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samun adadi da kuma adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 da aka sanar da kowace ƙasa a duniya ana sabunta su a kowace rana a karfe 8:00 na safe. Wannan adadi ana samun sa ne daga tushen hukuma kamar ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya ta ƙasar, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki, da WHO.
Ana amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a EU/EEA da UK, da kuma kwatanta shi da yanayin Italiya.
A matsayin wakilcin yaduwar cutar COVID-19 mai aiki, mun kirga abubuwan da suka faru na tsawon kwanaki 14, saboda haka muna la'akari da tafiyar COVID-19 ta al'ada, a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da aka ruwaito a kowace kasa har zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya
Yanayin abubuwan da suka faru na kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK sun yi daidai da yanayin da ke faruwa a lardin Hubei (Thailand) (Hoto 1).
Ga EU/EEA da UK gaba ɗaya, adadin COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ya ƙaru sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Abubuwan da aka ƙayyade).
Wannan yanayin ya samo asali ne daga saurin karuwar adadin wadanda aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan yanayin karuwar adadin COVID-19 (Additional Material).
Shafi na 2 ya nuna adadin adadin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK idan aka kwatanta da adadin da aka samu a Italiya a lokacin Janairu 31 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Bayanai sun nuna cewa, har zuwa 15 ga Maris, karfe 8:00, sauran ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin waɗanda suka yi daidai da adadin waɗanda suka yi daidai da Italiya makonni uku da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin rahoton COVID-19 na ƙaruwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya.
Yanayin da ake gani a cikin tarin abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar ta karu a daidai saurin a dukkan ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da bambancin matakan da kasashe ke fuskanta, bambancin martani na kiwon lafiyar jama'a, da yiwuwar bambancin ma'anar shari'ar tsakanin ƙasashe da bambancin ladabi don zaɓar marasa lafiya da za a gwada don tabbatar da COVID-19, wanda ya haɗa da gwajin biyo baya.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankin Italiya da abin ya shafa sun bayyana halin da ake ciki game da kashi 10% na marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai tsanani a yankin sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
A halin yanzu, ana samun bayanai game da karbar COVID-19 a asibitoci da/ko cibiyoyin kulawa mai tsanani a matakin EU/EAA na kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'i (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara bayanai a cikin tsari don kammala bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da kuma mutuwar.
Bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 2010-2011 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin wadatar gadajen jinya da na kula da lafiya a Turai, wanda ya kai daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a kowace dubu 100 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun albarkatu da yawa ko kaɗan fiye da Italiya (12.5 gadaje na kulawa mai mahimmanci da kulawa ta tsakiya a kowace 100,000 a cikin 2010-2011).
An samar da yanayin samfurin da ya danganci wadatar kulawar kiwon lafiya, tare da kimantawar yaduwar cutar COVID-19 a asibiti ga kowace EU/EEA da Burtaniya da ke da haɗarin >90% sama da ƙarfin gadajen kulawa mai tsanani, a cikin sabuntawa na shida na ECDC na saurin kimanta haɗarin COVID-19.
Tun da yake har zuwa yanzu an samu adadin mutane da suka kamu da cutar a wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya, kuma asibitoci da kuma cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa suna yawan yi wa jama'a hidima a wasu yankuna, ya kamata a samar da bayanai game da masu kamuwa da cutar da kuma wuraren kula da gaggawa a matakin Ƙididdigar Ƙungiyoyin Yanki na 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da yanayin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, jihohi, asibitoci, da na'urorin kula da gaggawa ya kamata su shirya don yanayin watsa SARS-CoV-2 na al'umma da kuma karuwar adadin marasa lafiyar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta kiwon lafiya, musamman kulawa mai tsanani, kamar yadda ya faru a yankunan da abin ya shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin rahoton ECDC na kwanan nan, hanzarin, hanzarin, da kuma cikakkiyar hanyar da za a bi na da muhimmanci wajen rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, tare da sauyawa daga tsarin hanawa zuwa tsarin ragewa, saboda karuwar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar, kamar yadda aka yi tsammani, na iya ba da isasshen lokaci ga masu yanke shawara da asibitoci don fahimtar, karɓa, da daidaitawa da amsa mai dacewa idan ba a aiwatar da shi ba.
Wannan saurin tantance hadarin ya kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokacin da za a iya ƙara inganta ƙoƙarin sarrafawa na SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ya gaza, tsarin kiwon lafiya na wasu ƙasashen EU/EEA na iya fuskantar hauhawar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Barkewar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda ta samo asali daga cutar coronavirus mai saurin numfashi mai saurin kamuwa da cuta 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ya zuwa yanzu ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ta kamu da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran sassan duniya, wanda hakan ya haifar da bala'i ga bil'adama.
Kamar kwayar cutar ta SARS-CoV, wadda ta haifar da cutar SARS a dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa daga batutuwan kuma yana haifar da irin wannan bayyanar ta hanyar irin wannan hanyar.
Duk da haka, COVID-19 yana da ƙananan matakan tsanani da mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yana da kamuwa da cuta kuma ya fi shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa, kuma ya fi shafar maza fiye da mata.
Domin a amsa yawan littattafan da ake wallafawa game da wannan sabon ciwo, wannan talifin ya yi ƙoƙari ya ba da cikakken bayani game da wannan ci gaba da ake samu a bincike.
Za mu tattauna muhimman abubuwa game da cututtuka, da ilmin halitta, da kuma ƙwayoyin cuta, da yadda ake ganewa da kuma magance su, da yadda ake ganewa da kuma yadda za a hana su.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba, muna fatan wannan binciken zai taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma kawar da wannan cuta mai barazana.
Bikin bazara a ranar 25 ga Janairu 2020 ya kasance abin tunawa da ba a taɓa gani ba ga duk Sinawa waɗanda aka umarce su da su zauna a gida yayin hutu da makonni bayan haka saboda barkewar sabuwar cutar kwayar cutar.
Kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) da ta haifar da barkewar cutar cutar sankarar hankula (SARS) a 2003; saboda haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya mata sunan SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma cutar da ta haifar an kira ta CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China, kuma ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa ko'ina cikin ƙasar da kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya.
Har zuwa 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da 80,000 na tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, tare da sama da 40,000 da aka mayar da su gida da kuma 3,000 da suka mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine "magabcin jama'a na 1" kuma yana da damar yin mummunan lalacewa fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu tun daga rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 wanda ya kafa jerin ƙwayoyin cuta da aka ware daga marasa lafiya da yawa, an buga takardu sama da 200 game da COVID-19, wanda ya shafi kwayar cuta, annoba, ilimin halittu, ganewar asali, da magani.
Wannan bita ya yi ƙoƙari ya taƙaita ci gaban bincike a cikin wannan sabon batun da ke ci gaba da sauri.
A inda ya yiwu, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma sauran cututtukan da ke haifar da CoV, wato ciwon numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, annobar cutar a shekarar 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya game da rigakafin cuta da kuma yadda ake gane ta, da kuma wasu tambayoyi da ba a amsa ba amma da suke da muhimmanci.
Bisa ga al'ada, CoVs ana ganin ba su da cutarwa ga mutane, musamman suna haifar da kusan kashi 15% na mura 4.
Duk da haka, a wannan karni, mun gano kwayar cutar ta Corona sau biyu, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, kowannensu ya haifar da barkewar cutar da ta fara a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012, kuma nan da nan ta bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da mummunan rashin lafiya da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 a halin yanzu shine annoba ta uku ta CoV a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a Hoto 1.1, an fara bayar da rahoton cluster pneumonia da ba a san asalinsa ba daga Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin.
Kwana bakwai bayan haka, an fitar da jerin kwayar cutar.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020, an ba da rahoton farkon mutuwar mutum daga Wuhan.
A lokacin, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa birane, larduna, da kuma ƙasashe da ke makwabtaka da ita.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an bayar da rahoton kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar masu kula da lafiya, wanda ke nuna cewa yiwuwar kamuwa da mutum-zuwa-mutum na iya faruwa.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an kafa dokar keɓewa a birnin Wuhan kuma an dakatar da dukkan hanyoyin sufuri.
A ranar 24 ga watan Janairu, binciken farko na asibiti kan cutar ya ruwaito cewa, daga cikin marasa lafiya 41 da aka tabbatar da su, marasa lafiya 21 ne kawai suka yi hulɗa kai tsaye da kasuwar abincin teku ta Wuhan wanda ake ganin wuri ne na farko na kamuwa da cutar daga asalin dabbobi da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, WHO ta ayyana annobar a matsayin gaggawa ta duniya.
A lokacin rubuta wannan rahoto, cutar ta bazu ko'ina cikin kasar Sin da kuma kusan kasashe 50 a duniya (Fig. 2).
Saboda yanayin da ke tasowa cikin sauri, har yanzu ba a tantance ainihin yanayin annobar ba.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, nazarin da aka yi a cibiyoyi da dama na marasa lafiya 8,866, wanda ya hada da 4,021 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, ya gabatar da wannan sabon tsarin annobar (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 na kamuwa da mutane a kowane zamani, amma musamman a tsakanin shekaru 30-65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na waɗanda suka kamu da cutar sun haura shekaru 50, kaɗan ne kawai shekarunsu ba su kai 20 ba, kuma mutane 14 ne kawai suka kamu da cutar ba su kai shekara 10 ba.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi cutar maza (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 na yaduwa a cikin gidajen abinci, musamman a ciki da kewayen Hubei.
COVID-19 yana ɗaukar matsakaicin kwanaki 5 (2-9) daga farawa zuwa ganewar asali.
Matsakaicin lokacin incubation shine kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Matsakaicin lokaci daga haihuwa zuwa mutuwa shine kwanaki 9.5 (4,8-13).
Adadin haihuwa na asali (R0) shine 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05) kuma R0 daidai yake da 2.23-4.82.
Adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ya karu sosai kafin 23 ga Janairu, 2020, daidai da lokacin manyan sufuri kafin bikin bazara a China.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya tare da tabbatar da shari'ar ta kasance 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%) da kuma mutuwar da aka yi daidai da shi ga dukkan marasa lafiya ta kasance 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Manyan abubuwan haɗari guda uku don COVID-19 su ne jinsi (maza), shekaru (≥60), da kuma ciwon huhu mai tsanani.
CoVs babban ƙaramin kwayar cutar kwayar cuta ne wanda ke ɗauke da zaren RNA guda ɗaya.
Ana iya rarraba CoVs zuwa jinsi huɗu, wato alpha, beta, gamma, da delta, tare da alfa- da beta-CoVs da aka sani suna cutar da mutane.
Glycoprotein na spike (S) na shinge yana haɗuwa da masu karɓar ƙwayoyin cuta, enzymes na canza angiotensin 2 (ACE 2) da dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) don SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, bi da bi, sannan membrane fusion ya faru.
An saki kwayar RNA ta kwayar cutar a cikin cytoplasm; bayan kwayar cutar ta kwayar cutar, RNA ta kwayar halitta tare da glycoprotein da kuma kwayar nucleocapsid sun samar da wani kwayar cuta mai dauke da virion, wanda daga baya ya hade da membrane na plasma don sakin kwayar cutar.
