Saboda haka, za mu iya komawa ga wasu binciken CoV da suka gabata, musamman SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV (Fig. 4).4).
Gabaɗaya, bayan mamayewar mai watsa shiri, kwayar cutar ta gano ta hanyar tsarin rigakafi ta hanyar masu karɓar tsarin ganewa (PRR), wanda ya haɗa da masu karɓar lectin-kamar C-type, masu karɓar Toll-like (TLR), masu karɓar NOD-like (NLR), da masu karɓar RIG-I-like (RLR).
Ta hanyar hanyoyi daban-daban, kwayar cutar tana haifar da bayyanar abubuwan kumburi, tsufa na kwayoyin dendritic, da kuma hadawar interferon nau'in I (IFN) wanda ke hana yaduwar kwayar cutar da kuma hanzarta maganin maganin kwayar cutar ta kwayar cutar ta kwayar cutar ta kwayar cutar.
