T lymphocytes, waɗanda suka haɗa da CD4+ da CD8+ suna da muhimmiyar rawa a wannan kāriya.
CD4+ T-cell tana motsa B-cell don samar da ƙwayoyin cuta da suka dace da cutar, kuma CD8+ T-cell tana kashe kwayoyin cutar kai tsaye.
T-cell mai taimako tana samar da cytokines masu hana kumburi don taimakawa kare sel.
