A kullum, mutanen da suka kamu da cutar a yawancin ko kuma waɗanda suke da matsalar aikin garkuwar jiki suna da damar kamuwa da cutar fiye da sauran mutane.
Kimanin matsakaicin lokacin incubation na SARS-CoV-2 shine kwanaki 1-14, mafi yawan kwanaki 3-7 bisa nazarin shari'o'in farko 425 a Wuhan.
Amma, nazarin mutane 1,099 ya nuna cewa matsakaicin lokacin da ake yi wa mutum ciki kwana uku ne kuma ya kai kwanaki 0 zuwa 24.
Wani sabon bincike, kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, ya nuna cewa lokacin incubation na kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2) bisa alƙaluma na mutane 8,866.
Yana da muhimmanci hukumomin kiwon lafiya su daidaita lokacin keɓewa bisa ga lokacin da aka fi dacewa na lokacin da ake kwantar da cutar domin hana mutane da ke da cutar, amma ba su da alamun cutar, su watsa cutar ga wasu.
A matsayin al'ada, ana bukatar a keɓe mutane na kwanaki 14 idan sun kamu da cutar ko kuma sun kamu da ita.
