Zazzabi sau da yawa shine farkon bayyanar COVID-19, tare ko ba tare da wasu alamun ba kamar su tari mai bushewa, numfashi mai wuya, ciwon tsoka, ciwon hanci, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, rhinorea, ciwon kirji, diarrhea, nausea, da kuma amai.
Wasu marasa lafiya suna samun dyspnea da/ ko hypoxemia mako guda bayan farawar cutar.
A cikin mawuyacin hali, ciwon mai haƙuri yana ci gaba da sauri zuwa ciwon numfashi mai tsanani, tashin hankali, acidosis na metabolic, da kuma coagulopathy.
Marasa lafiya da ke da zazzabi da/ko alamun numfashi da kuma zazzabi mai tsanani, koda kuwa ba tare da cutar cutar ba, ya kamata a yi musu gwajin kwayar cutar don ganewar asali.
Nazarin alƙaluma a ƙarshen Disamba 2019 ya nuna cewa yawan alamun cutar ya kai kashi 98% don zazzabi, 76% don tari mai bushe, 55% don dyspnea, da 3% don diarrhea; 8% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar taimakon ventilator.
An kuma samu irin wannan binciken a wasu bincike biyu da aka yi kwanan nan, wato nazarin da aka yi a kan dangin da kuma wanda aka yi a kan mutanen da ba su da iyalinsu.
A kwatankwacin haka, binciken alƙaluma a cikin 2012 ya nuna cewa marasa lafiyar MERS-CoV suma suna da zazzabi (98%), tari mai bushe (47%), da dyspnea (55%) a matsayin manyan alamun.
Koyaya, kashi 80% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar tallafin iska, fiye da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 kuma daidai da ƙimar mutuwar MERS fiye da COVID-19.
An kuma lura da zawo (26%) da ciwon makogwaro (21%) a cikin marasa lafiya na MERS.
A cikin marasa lafiya na SARS, zazzabi (99%-100%), tari mai bushe (29%-75%), dyspnea (40%-42%), diarrhea (20-25%), da ciwon makogwaro (13-25%) an nuna su a matsayin manyan alamun bayyanar kuma ana buƙatar tallafin iska don kusan 14%-20% na marasa lafiya.
