Akwai dogon tarihi na tattara jinin marasa lafiya da suka warke daga cututtuka masu yaduwa don a kula da wasu marasa lafiya da ke fama da irin wannan cutar ko kuma a hana mutane masu lafiya kamuwa da cutar.
