Yawancin abubuwan da ke da tasiri har yanzu ba a san su ba ko kuma ba su da tabbas saboda yana da wahala a cire ko tabbatar da waɗannan abubuwan ko haɗuwa mafi kyau.
A halin yanzu, saboda babu ingantaccen magani na musamman don COVID-19, TCM ya zama ɗayan manyan hanyoyin magani na madadin ga marasa lafiya masu saurin ciwo ko kuma ga mutanen da ke murmurewa daga mummunan cuta.
Misali, Shu Feng Jie Du da Lian Hua Qing Wen sun sami inganci wajen maganin COVID-19.
An lura da mafi girman adadin warkarwa a cikin maganin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a lardunan Sin da ke amfani da TCM a kashi 87% na marasa lafiya, wanda ya hada da Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), da Hunan (50%), yayin da lardin Hubei, wanda ke amfani da TCM a cikin kusan kashi 30% na marasa lafiya na COVID-19, yana da mafi ƙarancin adadin warkarwa (13%).
Duk da haka, wannan kwatancen har yanzu yana da matukar damuwa saboda yawancin abubuwan da ke haifar da tasiri, kamar yawan marasa lafiya da tsananin su, dole ne a haɗa su cikin kimantawa.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Boli Zhang da abokansa sun buga wani bincike wanda ya kwatanta maganin gargajiya na yamma (WM) kawai da maganin WM da TCM.
Sun gano cewa lokacin da ake bukata don dawo da zafin jiki, kawar da alamun, da kuma asibiti ya fi na WM+TCM yawa fiye da na WM kawai.
Abin mamaki, yawan cutarwa (daga mai sauƙi zuwa mai tsanani) ya kasance mafi ƙasƙanci ga ƙungiyar WM + TCM fiye da ƙungiyar WM kawai (7.4% vs. 46.2%) kuma ƙananan mutuwar a cikin ƙungiyar WM + TCM fiye da ƙungiyar WM kawai (8.8% vs. 39%).
Duk da haka, amfanin TCM da amincinsa suna jiran gwaji mai kyau a manyan sikelin da kuma cibiyoyin bincike da yawa.
Wani abu mai ban sha'awa shi ne bayyana tsarin aiki da kuma bayyana abubuwan da ke da tasiri a cikin maganin TCM ko kuma haɗuwa, idan ya yiwu.
