Bugu da ƙari, ƙaruwa na lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), da kuma creatine kinase (CK) na iya taimakawa wajen hango ƙarshen sakamako.
Ana bayyana waɗannan enzyme sosai a cikin gaɓoɓin jiki, musamman a zuciya da hanta, kuma ana sake su yayin lalacewar nama.
Saboda haka, waɗannan sunadaran sun kasance alamun gargajiya na rashin aiki na zuciya da hanta.
Babban bayyanar cututtuka: Za a yi la'akari da hotunan kirji da ci gaban bayyanar cututtuka na lokaci tare da wasu abubuwa don hango ƙarshen sakamako da rikitarwa na COVID-19.
Amfani da steroids: Kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, steroids su ne maganin hana rigakafi da ake amfani da su sosai a matsayin maganin tallafi ga cututtukan cututtuka don rage tsananin lalacewar kumburi.
Saboda ana amfani da magungunan corticosteroid masu yawa a cikin marasa lafiya masu cutar SARS, mutane da yawa da suka tsira daga cutar sun ƙare da shan cutar osteonecrosis avascular tare da nakasa rayuwa da kuma rashin ingancin rayuwa.
Saboda haka, idan ya zama dole, ya kamata a yi amfani da steroids a ƙananan allurai da gajeren lokaci a cikin marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
Damuwa ta hankali: Kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, a lokacin barkewar COVID-19, marasa lafiya da yawa sun sha wahala sosai saboda sun sami tsawan keɓewa da matsanancin rashin tabbas da kuma ganin mutuwar dangi na kusa da abokan su.
Ya kamata a ba da shawara ta ruhaniya da kuma tallafi na dogon lokaci don a taimaki wannan mai ciwo ya warke daga matsin kuma ya koma rayuwarsa ta yau da kullum.
