Duk da haka, a ranar 19 ga Janairu, 2020, daraktan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Wuhan ya kwantar da hankalin jama'a ta hanyar cewa sabon kwayar cutar tana da yanayin yaduwa da iyakantaccen damar haifuwa daga mutum zuwa mutum kuma rigakafin da kuma hana cutar ba matsala.
Wannan sakon ya kwantar da hankalin jama'a, musamman a lokacin da kasar ke shirin bikin bazara, don haka wannan lokaci mai mahimmanci ya wuce don hana cutar ta Wuhan.
Hukumar kula da cututtuka a China za ta yi koyi da wannan kuma ta yi gagarumin gyara a nan gaba.
Alal misali, ya kamata hukumar ta (1) kasance mai taka tsantsan wajen yin sanarwa ga jama'a domin kowane kalma tana sa mutane su kula kuma tana iya canza halinsu da shawarwarinsu; (2) ta kasance mai saukin kai da kuma amsawa ga bayanai da ba na al'ada ba daga asibitoci maimakon jiran rahoto na hukuma daga likitoci ko jami'ai masu iko; (3) ta kasance mai tsaurara don hana yiwuwar annoba a farkon matakai, maimakon ƙoƙarin kwantar da hankalin jama'a; kuma (4) ta fi yin atisaye masu manufa da tasiri don inganta wayar da kan jama'a game da annobar cutar da kuma gwadawa da inganta tsarin mayar da martani na jama'a a kai a kai.
Cutar COVID-19 ta samo asali ne daga sabon kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 wanda ya fara yaduwa a ƙarshen Disamba 2019.
A cikin kasa da watanni biyu, annobar ta bazu ko'ina cikin kasar Sin da kuma kasashe sama da 50 a duniya a lokacin da nake rubuta wannan bita.
Saboda kwayar cutar ta yi kama da SARS-CoV kuma alamun COVID-19 da SARS sun yi kama, barkewar COVID-19 na da alama kamar annobar SARS ta sake faruwa.
Duk da haka, akwai wasu bambance-bambance masu ban mamaki tsakanin COVID-19 da SARS, waɗanda suke da mahimmanci wajen shawo kan annobar da kuma kula da marasa lafiya.
COVID-19 ya fi shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa kuma ya fi shafar maza fiye da mata, kuma yawan mutuwar tsofaffi ya fi na matasa.
Mutuwar SARS ta fi ta COVID-19 (10.91% vs. 1.44%).
Marasa lafiya COVID-19 suna watsa kwayar cutar koda kuwa ba su da alamun cutar, yayin da marasa lafiya SARS galibi suna watsa kwayar cutar lokacin da suke da mummunan rashin lafiya. Wannan yana haifar da babbar wahala wajen hana yaduwar COVID-19 fiye da SARS.
Wannan ya bayyana wani ɓangare na dalilin da yasa SARS-CoV-2 ke yaduwa cikin sauri da kuma yaduwa fiye da SARS-CoV.
Gwajin RNA na yau da kullun don bincika SARS-CoV-2 na iya haifar da sakamako mara kyau a cikin wasu marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
A wani bangare kuma, marasa lafiya da suka warke za su iya sake nuna tabbatacce a gwajin cutar.
Wannan binciken ya kara hadarin yaduwar cutar.
Tare da saurin ci gaban binciken COVID-19, wasu mahimman batutuwa har yanzu suna buƙatar warwarewa, wato:
Daga ina SARS-CoV-2 ya fito?
Duk da cewa an gano daidaiton kwayoyin halittar kashi 96 cikin dari tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da kuma wasu nau'in SARS-CoVs guda biyu na bat, har yanzu ba mu iya kammala cewa SARS-CoV-2 ya fito ne daga bat ba.
Waɗanne dabbobi ne suke aiki a matsayin matsakaici wajen watsa ƙwayoyin cuta daga mahaifinsu, kamar su bat, zuwa ga mutane?
Idan ba mu san amsoshin 1 da 2 ba, ba za mu iya kashe watsawar yadda ya kamata ba kuma annoba za ta iya sake yaduwa a kowane lokaci.
Ko da yake samfurin kwayoyin halitta da asalin kwayoyin halitta sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da alaƙa da ACE2, ta yaya ainihin kwayar cutar ta shiga cikin ƙwayoyin numfashi kuma ta haifar da canje-canje na pathological?
Shin wannan kwayar cutar tana da alaka da kwayoyin dake bayyana ACE2 a wasu gabobin jiki?
Idan ba tare da amsoshin waɗannan tambayoyin ba, ba za mu iya samun saurin ganewar asali da kuma magani mai kyau ba.
Har yaushe za a ci gaba da wannan annobar?
Ta yaya kwayar cutar take girma a cikin kwayoyin halittar mutum?
Shin za ta zama annoba ta duniya, ta ƙare kamar SARS, ko kuma za ta sake faruwa a kai a kai kamar mura?
Amsoshin waɗannan tambayoyin da kuma wasu da yawa suna da muhimmanci, amma suna iya ɗaukan lokaci kafin a samu.
Duk da haka, ko da menene farashin, ba mu da wani zaɓi sai dai mu dakatar da annobar da wuri-wuri don mu koma ga rayuwa ta yau da kullun.
Tushen cutar korona ta mutum
Shekaru dubbai, sauye-sauye da kuma daidaitawa sun motsa co-juyin halitta na kwayar cutar korona (CoV) da mai masaukin ta, gami da mutane.
Kafin 2003, an san cewa kwayar cutar mutum (HCoV) biyu tana haifar da cututtuka masu saurin kamuwa da cuta, kamar mura.
Annobar cutar sankarar numfashi (SARS) da cutar sankarar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun juya al'amarin kuma sun nuna yadda kamuwa da kwayar HCoV za ta iya zama mai hallaka da barazana ga rai.
Yunƙurin SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ya sake sanya CoV a cikin haske kuma ya ba mu mamaki tare da yawan watsawa, amma tare da ƙananan cututtukan cututtukan da ɗan'uwansa, SARS-CoV.
Cutar HCoVs cuta ce ta dabbobi, saboda haka fahimtar asalin HCoVs zai taimaka mana.
Yawancin kwayar cutar HCoVs sun fito ne daga bat. A cikin waɗannan dabbobi, kwayar cutar ba ta da cutar.
An kuma san cibiyar ajiyar wasu HCoVs.
Gano mahaifar dabba yana da tasiri kai tsaye a rigakafin cutar ɗan adam.
Binciken hulɗar CoV-guga a cikin dabbobi na iya ba da muhimmiyar fahimta game da cutar CoV a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, mun gabatar da cikakken bayani game da ilimin da ake da shi a yanzu game da kwayar cutar HCoVs bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da kuma asalin su na dabbobi da kuma yaduwar su tsakanin jinsuna.
Abu mai mahimmanci, mun gwada kuma mun bambanta HCoVs daga ra'ayi na juyin halitta da kuma sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta.
An tattauna game da annobar cutar CoV 2019 (COVID-19) a wannan mahallin.
Bugu da ƙari, an kuma ba da haske game da bukatun sauyawar mai watsa shiri da kuma tasirin juyin halitta na kwayar cutar akan tsananin cutar.
Kwayar cutar korona (CoV) ta fito ne daga dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na ƙwayoyin cuta masu ɓoye, masu kyau, da kuma RNA guda ɗaya.
Wannan kwayar tana da kwayar halitta mafi girma da girman 26 zuwa 32 kilobase a tsakanin kwayar RNA da ake kira "CoV", saboda yanayin jikinta da ke kama da kambi a ƙarƙashin allon lantarki.
Bisa ga tsarin, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halittar da ba su da rarrabuwa da ke da tsari iri ɗaya.
Kusan kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta sun ƙunshi manyan tsarin karatu guda biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b) waɗanda suka haɗu da juna.
Polyprotein yana fuskantar ƙarin sarrafawa don ƙirƙirar 16 ba tare da tsari ba, wanda ake kira nsp1~16.
Sauran genomes sun ƙunshi tsarin karantawa na buɗe (ORF) don sunadarai na tsari, wanda ya haɗa da spikes (S), sheqa (E), membrane (M), da nucleoprotein (N).
Wasu sunadarai masu amfani da keɓaɓɓun layin sun kuma ƙunsar da layin CoV daban-daban.
Dangane da bambance-bambance a jerin sunayen sunadarai, an rarraba CoVs zuwa jinsi huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, da delta-CoV); daga cikin waɗannan nau'ikan huɗu, nau'in beta-CoV yana da mafi yawan HCoVs kuma an sake raba shi zuwa layi huɗu (A, B, C, da D).
Shaidar phylogenetic ta nuna cewa bat da rodents sune tushen yawancin kwayoyin alpha-CoV da beta-CoV, yayin da tsuntsaye sune babban ma'ajiyar gamma-CoV da delta-CoV.
Shekaru dubbai, CoVs suna ci gaba da ƙetare shingen jinsin kuma wasu CoVs sun zama muhimman cututtuka ga mutane.
Ya zuwa yanzu, an san mutane bakwai da ke dauke da kwayar cutar korona (HCoVs).
Daga cikin kwayar cutar guda bakwai, HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alpha-CoVs.
Sauran beta-CoV guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, kwayar cutar coronavirus na cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV), kwayar cutar coronavirus na cututtukan numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV), da SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, da HCoV-NL63 yawanci suna haifar da ƙananan alamun, kamar sanyi da/ko zawo.
Akasin haka, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, da SARS-CoV-2 suna da cututtuka sosai, suna haifar da kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar numfashi a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa kuma suna da damar da za su iya zama cututtukan cututtukan numfashi (ARDS) da bayyanar da ke bayan gabobin huhu.
An gano kwayar HCoV-229E ta farko, B814, daga cikin marasa lafiya da suka kamu da cutar sanyi a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin ilimi ta hanyar zurfin nazarin HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, waɗanda duka biyu ke haifar da bayyanar cututtuka da kansu.
A gaskiya, an yarda da cewa kamuwa da kwayar HCoV ba ta da haɗari, har sai da barkewar cutar SARS.
Barnar SARS da ta auku a 2003 tana ɗaya daga cikin munanan annobar cutar a tarihin zamani, ta cutar da mutane fiye da 8,000 da yawan mutuwar kusan 10%.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, annobar cutar MERS ta Gabas ta Tsakiya ta haifar da ci gaba da barkewar cutar a yankin Larabawa tare da yaduwar ta a wasu sassan duniya.
Sabuwar kwayar cutar HCoV ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), wanda aka sani da SARS-CoV-2, shine mai haddasa annobar cutar korona ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ta kashe mutane sama da 3,120 kuma ta kamu da mutane sama da 91,000 har zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi gargadin cewa duniya za ta shirya don annobar SARS-CoV-2 mai zuwa.
Dukkanin kwayar cutar HCoVs bakwai suna da asalin zoonotic daga bat, mice, ko dabbobi.
Akwai shaidar da ta nuna cewa dukkanin kwayar cutar HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga bat. A cikin bat, CoVs suna da kyau kuma ba su da cutar, amma suna nuna bambancin kwayoyin halitta.
Annobar COVID-19 ta haifar da ƙalubale na musamman na likita, kimiyya, zamantakewa, da ɗabi'a ga China da sauran duniya.
Binciken asalin kwayar cutar HCoV ya ba da tsari don fahimtar tarihin halitta, motsa jiki, da abubuwan da ke hana yiwuwar motsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
Wannan binciken kuma na iya jagorantar ko sauƙaƙa binciken mai watsa shiri na SARS-CoV-2 na tanadi, matsakaici, da kuma fadadawa, wanda ke da muhimmiyar ma'ana a cikin hana yaduwar nan gaba.
A cikin wannan bita, mun ba da cikakken bayani game da asalin zoonotic, watsawa tsakanin jinsuna, da kuma cutar HCoV.
Mun ba da haske musamman kuma mun tattauna batun gama gari cewa kwayar cutar HCoV ta saba zama ba kwayar cuta ba a cikin taskar halitta, amma ta zama kwayar cuta bayan watsawa tsakanin jinsuna zuwa sabon mai masaukin baki.
Mun kuma duba yanayin juyin HCoV cewa ƙaruwar iyawar watsawa sau da yawa yana tare da raguwar cutar.
An kuma tattauna sakamakon cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin wannan mahallin.
An san kwayar cutar dabbobi tun daga ƙarshen shekarun 1930.
Kafin warewar HCoV-229E na farko na B814 daga cikin mutanen da suka kamu da mura, an gano CoVs da yawa daga dabbobi da yawa da suka kamu da cutar, wadanda suka hada da turke, beraye, shanu, aladu, kuliyoyi, da karnuka.
A cikin shekarun baya-bayan nan, an gano kwayar cutar HCoV guda bakwai.
Takaitaccen tarihin gano HCoVs cikin tsari na lokaci (Table 1) yana da bayani.
An fara ware kwayar HCoV-229E daga cikin numfashi na marasa lafiya da ke fama da kamuwa da cutar numfashi a shekarar 1966, wanda daga baya aka tsara shi don girma a cikin layin kwayar cutar huhu WI-38.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da HCoV-229E suna nuna alamun sanyi, wanda ya hada da ciwon kai, tari, kumburi, da ciwon makogwaro, tare da zazzabi da tari wanda aka gani a cikin 10~20% na lokuta.
Daga baya a 1967, an ware HCoV-OC43 daga al'adun gabobin da kuma jerin hanyoyin da aka tsara a cikin kwakwalwar jariri mai shayarwa.
Bayanan asibiti na kamuwa da cutar HCoV-OC43 sun yi kama da kamuwa da cutar da HCoV-229E ke haifarwa, wanda ba shi da bambanci da cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan numfashi kamar su kwayar cutar mura A da rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 sun yadu a duniya kuma suna iya yaduwa sosai a lokacin hunturu a yankunan da ke da yanayin zafi.
Yawancin lokaci, lokacin da kwayar cutar take kwance a cikin ƙasa da mako guda, sai kuma a yi rashin lafiya na tsawon makonni biyu.
Bisa ga binciken masu ba da kai na ɗan adam, mutane masu lafiya waɗanda ke kamuwa da HCoV-229E suna da ɗan sanyi.
Ƙananan marasa lafiya da suke da rauni a tsarin garkuwar jiki ne kawai suke nuna kamuwa da cutar numfashi.
SARS, wanda aka fi sani da "atypical pneumonia", shi ne farkon annobar cutar HCoV da aka rubuta a tarihin ɗan adam kuma kwayar cutar SARS-CoV ce, wanda shine HCoV na uku da aka gano.
Ana iya gano farkon cutar SARS a ƙarshen 2002 a lardin Guangdong na kasar Sin.
Cutar SARS ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar mutum 8,096 da mutuwar mutum 774, a kasashe da nahiyoyi da dama.
Baya ga superinfectious, kowane yanayi ana tsammanin zai iya haifar da kusan yanayi biyu na biyu, tare da lokacin incubation na kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 kuma ana iya ganin ƙaruwar ƙwayar cutar a ranar 10 na cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da SARS-CoV sun fara fuskantar rashin tausayi, ciwon kai, zazzabi, rashin motsi, da kuma jin ƙanƙantar jiki, wanda ya biyo bayan dyspnea, tari, da kuma rashin numfashi a matsayin alamun ci gaba.
Lymphopenia, rashin aikin hanta, da kuma ƙaruwar creatinine kinase su ne cututtukan da ake samu a cikin SARS.
An kuma lura da lalacewar yaduwar alveolar, yaduwar ƙwayoyin epithelial, da kuma ƙaruwa na macrophage a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS.
Bugu da ƙari, kusan kashi 20-30% na marasa lafiya suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani da kuma na'ura mai sarrafa iska.
Ban da ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi, wasu gabobin da suka haɗa da gastrointestinal tract, hanta, da kuma ƙwayoyin cuta suna iya kamuwa da cuta a cikin matsanancin yanayi, yawanci tare da hadarin cytokines, wanda zai iya zama mai kisa, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya marasa ƙarfi.
An fara gano kwayar cutar ne daga wani dan uwan da aka yi masa kwayar cutar a cikin wani wuri da aka bude wanda ya yi tafiya zuwa Hong Kong daga Guangzhou.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an yi ƙoƙari sosai wajen binciken HCoV.
An ware HCoV-NL63 daga jariri mai wata 7 daga Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
A farko, wannan cuta ta fi yawa a cikin yara, tsofaffi, da marasa lafiya masu rauni da ke fama da cututtukan numfashi.
Bayani na choriitis, conjunctivitis, zazzabi, da bronchiolitis ana samun su a cikin cututtukan da HCoV-NL63 ke haifarwa.
Wani bincike na 'yanci ya bayyana cewa an ware irin wannan kwayar cutar daga kwayar hanci na wani yaro mai wata takwas da ke fama da ciwon huhu a Netherlands.
Ko da yake an gano shi a Netherlands, amma a gaskiya ya yaɗu a duk duniya.
An kiyasta cewa HCoV-NL63 yana wakiltar kusan kashi 4.7% na cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun kuma mafi girman abubuwan da ke faruwa suna faruwa a farkon bazara, bazara, da hunturu.
HCoV-NL63 yana da alaƙa da cutar laringitis ta hanawa, wanda kuma ake kira croup.
A wannan shekarar, an gano HCoV-HKU1 daga wani mutum mai shekaru 71 da aka kwantar da shi a asibiti saboda ciwon huhu da kuma cutar sankarar bargo a Hong Kong.
Baya ga cutar huhu da kuma cutar ta ƙwayar cuta, an ba da rahoton HCoV-HKU1 da ke da alaƙa da matsanancin cutar asma.
Kamar HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E, da HCoV-OC43, ana samun HCoV-HKU1 a duk duniya, yana haifar da rashin lafiya na numfashi.
Duk da haka, ba a san dalilin da ya sa wasu cututtuka masu yawa ba su faru ba, kamar yadda aka yi a cikin cutar HCoV-NL63 mai cutarwa wanda aka ba da rahoton kwanan nan yana haifar da kamuwa da cutar numfashi a cikin kasar Sin.
Gabaɗaya, lokacin da aka sami damar motsawa cikin inganci da ci gaba da riƙe kansa a cikin ɗan adam, cutar da cutar HCoVs ɗin ma sun ragu.
An fara gano kwayar cutar MERS-CoV a shekarar 2012 daga huhu na wani mutum mai shekaru 60 da ke fama da ciwon huhu da kuma rashin aikin koda a Saudi Arabiya.
Kodayake yawancin lab-tabbatattun magungunan sun fito ne daga Gabas ta Tsakiya, an samu rahoton shigo da magungunan tare da wasu lokuta na watsawa zuwa wasu kasashen Turai da Tunisia.
Wani barkewar cutar ta biyu ya faru ne a Koriya ta Kudu a shekarar 2015 inda aka tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar mutum 186.
Bayyanar asibiti na MERS yayi kama da bayyanar asibiti na SARS, wanda ke nuna ci gaba da ciwon huhu mai tsanani.
Ba kamar SARS ba, yawancin masu fama da cutar MERS suna fama da rashin ciwon koda, wanda ya zuwa yanzu ya kasance kawai a cikin cutar MERS tsakanin cututtukan da HCoV ke haifarwa.
Fiye da kashi 30 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya suna nuna alamun ciwon ciki, kamar su diarrhea da kuma amai.
Har zuwa 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, an bayar da rahoton fiye da lambobi 2500 da aka tabbatar da su tare da mutuwar mutane da yawa, wato kashi 34.4%, wanda ya sanya MERS-CoV daya daga cikin cututtukan da suka fi kowa tsoro da aka sani ga ɗan adam.
A tsakiyar zuwa ƙarshen Disamba 2019, an gano wani gungun marasa lafiya na ciwon huhu wanda aka danganta da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana cewa annobar cutar numfashi ta ƙasa da ke gudana da kuma SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin Matsalar Lafiya ta Duniya kuma ta sanya sunan cutar COVID-19.
Har zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020, an tabbatar da shari'o'i 90,053 a duk duniya, tare da mutuwar marasa lafiya da kashi 3.4%.
A lura, mutuwar cutar a Hubei, China, ya kai kashi 4.2%, yayin da mutuwar cutar a wajen Hubei ya kai kashi 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 na haifar da kamuwa da cuta mai tsanani kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV tare da bayyanar zazzabi, tari, da kuma numfashi mai wuya.
An kuma samu zawo a wasu marasa lafiya.
Ciwon huhu yana cikin alamun da suka fi tsanani kuma yana iya saurin zama ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
Kodayake SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da kamanceceniya sosai saboda babban daidaiton tsarin nucleotide, na 82%, dukansu sun kasance cikin rassan bishiyar phylogenetic daban.
Pathogenicity na SARS-CoV-2 a bayyane yake ya fi ƙasa, amma ya fi yaduwa idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
An samu rahoton mutane da ke kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ba tare da wata alama ba kuma wataƙila sun taka rawa wajen saurin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 a duniya.
Kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da kuma bambance-bambance da sauran HCoVs shida ya nuna kamance da bambance-bambance masu ban sha'awa.
