Mutane za su iya raba wurin da suke da shi da namomin kaza ta wajen kashe su ko kuma hakar kwal.
Na biyu, tsuntsayen tsuntsaye na iya zama ɗaya daga cikin masu watsa shirye-shiryen watsa shirye-shiryen watsa shirye-shiryen SARS-CoV-2 da suka shigo.
Mutane sun kamu da cutar ta hanyar yanka da cin naman da aka kashe.
Wataƙila, dabbobi masu shayarwa da yawa, waɗanda suka haɗa da dabbobin gida, suna da saukin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2.
Ana bukatar a yi gwajin rigakafi a kan dabbobin gida da kuma dabbobin daji.
Na uku, kamar yadda aka ambata a sama, sake haɗuwa da daidaitawa na SARS-CoV-2 na iya faruwa a cikin nau'in nau'in na uku wanda ke hulɗa da duka bat da tsuntsaye.
Binciken asalin dabbobi na SARS-CoV-2 na ci gaba.
Baya ga nau'ikan dabbobi masu ba da izini, manyan abubuwa uku na ɓangarorin kwayar cutar suna da mahimmanci don sauƙaƙe wa CoVs su ƙetare shingen nau'in.
Na farko, saurin canjin da suke yi a kwafin RNA.
Idan aka kwatanta da sauran ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA guda ɗaya, ƙididdigar ƙimar canjin CoV za a iya ɗauka matsakaici zuwa high tare da matsakaicin sauyawar sau ~10-4 a kowace shekara a kowane wuri, dangane da matakin daidaitawar CoV zuwa sabon mai masaukin.
CoVs suna da exoribonuclease mai gyara, kawarwa wanda ke haifar da ƙaruwa mai yawa, attenuation, ko ma inviability.
Abin sha'awa, an san cewa analog na Remdesivir yana hana kwayar cutar CoV ta hanyar hana wannan exoribonuclease da RNA-dependent RNA polymerase.
Remdesivir yana ɗaya daga cikin magungunan anti-SARS-CoV-2 da suka fi ba da tabbaci da za a gwada a gwaji.
Duk da haka, canjin CoV ya ninka na mai shi sau miliyan.
Bugu da ƙari, yawan canjin sau da yawa yana da girma yayin da CoVs ba su daidaita da mahaifinsu ba.
Idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoVs waɗanda ke da saurin canji, saurin canjin SARS-CoV-2 ya yi ƙasa, yana nuna cewa ya fi dacewa da ɗan adam.
Wataƙila, SARS-CoV-2 ya daidaita da wasu runduna da ke da kusanci da mutane.
Baya ga SARS-CoV-2, wannan kuma ya shafi MERS-CoV wanda ya daidaita da raƙuman Arabiya.
A ka'ida, akwai yiwuwar cewa canjin kwayoyin zai sa allurar rigakafi da kuma maganin rigakafin cutar SARS-CoV-2 su zama marasa tasiri.
Na biyu, babban kwayar RNA a cikin CoVs na ba da ƙarin sassauci a gyaran kwayar halitta, don canzawa da sake haɗawa, don haka yana ƙara yiwuwar co-juyin halitta tsakanin jinsuna, wanda ke da fa'ida ga bayyanar sabbin CoVs lokacin da yanayi ya dace.
Wannan yana da goyon baya ta hanyar yawan takamaiman tsarin karantawa da kuma aikin da aka tsara na furotin zuwa ƙarshen 3′ na genomes.
Na uku, CoVs suna sauya samfuri ba zato ba tsammani yayin kwafin RNA ta hanyar tsarin select-salin na musamman.
A cikin mai masaukin da ke aiki a matsayin mai hadawa, sauya zaren yana faruwa sau da yawa yayin fassarar RNA na CoV.
Cikakken RNA da kuma RNA mai yawan kama-da-wane na iya sake haɗuwa don samar da sabon CoV.
An sami tabbacin phylogenetic na sake haɗuwa ta halitta a cikin HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-OC43, haka kuma a cikin CoV na dabbobi kamar su SL-CoV na bat da CoV-HKU9 na bat.
Haɗin gwiwar kwayar cutar a cikin hulɗa da watsawa
Baya ga abubuwan da aka ambata a sama, hulɗar kwayar cutar da mai karɓar mai watsawa wani babban abu ne wanda ke shafar watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
A nan, ana ɗaukar sake haɗuwa da SARS-CoV a matsayin misali na musamman, wanda kuma ya nuna shaidar zaɓi mai kyau yayin faruwar watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
Dangane da nazarin kwatancen tsakanin kwayar cutar SARS-CoV na ɗan adam da na fox, ana zargin SARS-CoV yana yin saurin daidaitawa a cikin yawancin mahalarta, musamman tare da maye gurbin RBD na furotin S.
A yadda aka saba, kwayar cutar S CoV mai suna RBD tana hulɗa da masu karɓar ƙwayoyin cuta kuma tana zama maƙasudin amsawar kwayar cutar.
A cikin SARS-CoV, RBD shine amino acid na 318 zuwa 510 a kan S1 fragment, wanda ke da alaƙa da ACE2 na ɗan adam da kuma masu karɓar sa a matsayin hanyar shiga kwayar cutar.
RBD SARS-CoV yana da ikon gane masu karɓar ACE2 na dabbobi daban-daban, waɗanda suka haɗa da bat, fox, mice, da raccoon, don haka yana ba da damar watsa kwayar cutar tsakanin jinsuna.
A gaskiya, kawai 6 amino acid residues aka lura daban-daban tsakanin mutum da fox virus isolate a RBD da kuma 4 daga cikinsu suna located a cikin mahaɗin mahaɗin haɗi don hulɗa tare da ACE2 mai karɓa.
SARS-CoV fox yana da sauye-sauyen K479N da S487T a cikin RBD, wanda zai iya haɓaka alaƙar hulɗar furotin tare da mai karɓar ACE2 na ɗan adam.
A wasu kalmomi, waɗannan amino acid biyu na maye gurbin na iya zama da muhimmanci ga yadda kwayar cutar take daidaitawa ga mutane.
Ya kamata a lura cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da masu karɓar kwayar halitta iri ɗaya da SARS-CoV.
Bambanci na 30% tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da SARS-CoV a cikin S1 na S sunadarai yana nuna cewa ƙirar haɗin S sunadarai tare da ACE2 na ɗan adam na iya canzawa.
A gaskiya ma, wani binciken cryo-EM ya nuna cewa alaƙar ACE2 na ɗan adam da SARS-CoV-2 S sun ninka sau 10 zuwa 20 fiye da alaƙar ACE2 na ɗan adam da SARS-CoV S.
Abu mai mahimmanci kuma da za a sani shine ko akwai wasu masu karɓar karɓa waɗanda za a iya buƙata don watsa SARS-CoV-2.
Abin sha'awa, HCoV-NL63 kuma yana da alaƙa da ACE2, amma tare da wani ɓangare daban a cikin S.
Akwai sauran masu karɓar HCoV da yawa, kamar aminopeptidase N don HCoV-229E da kuma 9-O-therasethylated sialic acid don HCoV-OC43.
Waɗannan masu karɓa na iya taka rawa a nasarar daidaita wannan CoV a cikin ɗan adam bayan watsawa tsakanin jinsuna daga mai masaukin dabbobi.
Baya ga masu karɓar ƙwayoyin cuta, sakamakon watsa HCoV tsakanin jinsuna kuma ana sarrafa shi ta wasu abubuwan dogaro da ƙuntatawa na mai masaukin baki.
Wannan bambancin da ke tsakanin mutanen da suke da furotin da ke cikin gidajen abinci na halitta, kamar su bat da Arabian camels da kuma rodents, zai iya zama wani shinge ga watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
HCoVs dole ne su ɗauki nauyin dogara ga mai masaukin baki kuma su keta abubuwan hanawa na mai masaukin baki don samun nasara a watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
A wannan yanayin, dole ne a gano kuma a bayyana abubuwan da ke sa abubuwa su kasance a cikin kwayoyin da ke cikin wannan muhimmin wuri na hulɗa tsakanin ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma masu gida.
Yin amfani da fasahar CRISPR mai saurin gaske na iya zama da amfani wajen tace dukkanin kwayoyin halittar don duba abubuwan dogaro da kuma hana SARS-CoV-2 mai gida.
Sabon HCoV ya bayyana: komawar farkon barkewar cutar
Bambancin CoV na bat yana ba da babbar dama ga fitowar sabbin HCoVs.
A wannan yanayin, CoV na bat yana aiki a matsayin ɓoye na HCoV.
Bugu da ƙari, saurin canzawa da kuma sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta sun kuma motsa juyin HCoVs kuma suna aiki a matsayin matakai biyu masu mahimmanci a cikin wannan tsari.
Alal misali, samun ko rasa sabon kwayar halittar mai maye gurbin kwayar cutar na iya canja fasalin kwayar cutar sosai.
A cikin sunadarai masu amfani da SARS-CoV, ana tsammanin ORF8 yana da muhimmiyar rawa wajen daidaitawa ga ɗan adam saboda an gano kwayar cutar bat-SARS-CoV da aka ware tana ƙin wasu sunadarai na ORF8.
SARS-CoV mai fasalin kawar da kwayar cuta 29 an gano shi a cikin wani nau'in da aka ware a farkon barkewar cutar a cikin mutane.
Wannan cirewar ya raba ORF8 zuwa ORF8a da ORF8b kuma ana zaton yana da maye gurbin maye gurbin da ke tallafawa sauyawar mai masaukin baki.
Bugu da ƙari, SARS-CoV na iya samun tarihin haɗuwa tare da layin alfa-CoV da gamma-CoV, tare da gano ƙananan ƙananan ƙananan yankuna a cikin RNA polymerase wanda ya dogara da RNA.
An kuma gano wuraren sake haɗuwa a cikin nsp9, yawancin nsp10, da kuma wasu nsp14.
Hakazalika, an nuna cewa an samu sake haɗuwa tsakanin zuriya daban-daban a cikin annobar MERS-CoV, wadda ta faru a cikin raƙuman Arabiya a Saudi Arabiya.
Baya ga SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, an kuma lura da abubuwan da ke faruwa a cikin wasu HCoVs inda HCoVs ke sake haɗuwa da wasu CoVs na dabbobi a cikin ƙwayoyin halittar su.
Ya kamata a lura cewa zaɓin wucin gadi na iya taka rawa a cikin canje-canje na ba da gangan a cikin kwayar cutar, mai yiwuwa ta hanyar sakin kwayar cutar daga matsin zaɓin da ta fuskanta, kamar ta tsarin garkuwar jiki na mai masaukin baki.
Misali na wannan tasirin shine asarar ORF4 gaba ɗaya a cikin kwayar cutar HCoV-229E ta hanyar cire nucleotides biyu.
Yayin da ORF4 mai cikakke za a iya lura da shi a cikin bat da camel viruses da ke da alaƙa da HCoV-229E, alpha-CoV alpaca yana nuna shigar da nucleotide guda ɗaya wanda ke haifar da sauya fasalin.
A ƙarshe, an kuma motsa juyin halittar sabon HCoV ta matsin zaɓin a cikin rukunin mai masaukin.
An gano rashin bayyanar cututtuka ko kuma rashin bayyanar cututtuka lokacin da batutuwan suka kamu da CoV, wanda ke nuna daidaituwa tsakanin CoV da batutuwan.
Ya bayyana cewa batutuwan sun dace da CoV sosai ta fuskar jiki da kuma jiki.
Alal misali, rashin aiki a kunna amsa mai hana kumburi a cikin bat zai rage cutar da ke haifar da CoV sosai.
Bugu da ƙari, aikin kwayar halitta a cikin bat an matse shi saboda ƙaruwar tsarin ƙwayoyin halitta na kwayar halitta mai hanawa NKG2/CD94 da ƙananan ƙididdigar ƙididdigar ƙwayoyin cuta na Histocompatibility na farko.
Bugu da ƙari, yawan nau'in oxygen mai saurin motsa jiki (ROS) na ayyukan metabolism na bat zai iya hana kwafin CoVs kuma ya shafi gyaran da exoribonuclease ke yi don haka ya ba da matsin lamba don ƙirƙirar kwayar cutar mai saurin kamuwa da cuta lokacin da ta shiga cikin sabon mai masaukin.
Ƙarin kwayar cuta ta CoV na iya haɓaka ta hanyar sake haɗuwa, wanda ke haifar da samun sabon furotin ko fasalin furotin don daidaitawar mai masaukin baki.
Saboda haka, ba daidaituwa ba ce cewa sababbin ƙwayoyin cuta guda uku sun bayyana a cikin shekaru ashirin da suka gabata.
CoVs ba su da cutar ko kuma suna haifar da ƙananan alamu a cikin mahalarta, kamar su bat da raƙumi.
CoVs suna yin kwafi sosai ba tare da haifar da amsawar garkuwar jiki mai ƙarfi ba.
Wannan shi ne asirin da ke tattare da kamuwa da cuta a cikin mutane.
Alamun suna da tsanani musamman saboda yawan kunnawar amsawar rigakafi da kuma guguwar cytokine, tare da lalacewar huhu da ke da tsanani idan amsawar rigakafin ta yi ƙarfi.
Akasin haka, a cikin masu dauke da cutar da ba su da alamun cutar, amsawar garkuwar jikin ta rabu da kwayar cutar.
Irin wannan dabarar don yanke shawarar alaƙar amsawar rigakafi na iya zama da amfani a cikin maganin anti-SARS-CoV-2.
Amsar interferon tana da ƙarfi musamman a cikin bat.
Saboda haka, bayar da interferon nau'in I, aƙalla a farkon kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin mutane, ya kamata ya zama da amfani.
Bugu da ƙari, kunnawar NLRP3 na kumburi a cikin bat yana da lahani.
Saboda wannan dalili, hana NLRP3 na kumburi tare da MCC950 na iya zama da amfani wajen kula da COVID-19.
Bayyanar SARS-CoV-2 ta bi hanyar bayyanar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
Yayin da aka gano beta-CoVs na bat da ke raba kashi 95% na kwayar cutar tare da SARS-CoV, an kuma gano CoVs na bat da ke raba kashi 96% na kwayar cutar tare da SARS-CoV-2.
Ko da yake an gano cewa foxes da sauran dabbobi a kasuwa suna dauke da kwayar cutar da ta yi daidai da SARS-CoV, ba a gano wani mai watsa shiri na kai tsaye ga SARS-CoV-2 ba.
An gano beta-CoV na albasa mai matukar kama da SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke nuna cewa albasa na iya taka rawa a matsayin daya daga cikin mahalarta matsakaici ko kuma beta-CoV na albasa na iya ba da gudummawar wani yanki na kwayoyin halitta a cikin sigar ƙarshe ta SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da cewa har yanzu ana ta tambaya, babu wata hujja da ta nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 na mutum ne ko dai da gangan ko kuma ba da gangan ba.
CoVs sun sake zama abin lura saboda annobar SARS-CoV-2 da ta faru kwanan nan.
Nazarin CoVs a cikin bat da sauran dabbobi ya canza ra'ayinmu game da mahimmancin asalin dabbobi da kuma ma'adinan dabbobi don HCoVs a cikin watsawa ga mutane.
Akwai tabbaci mai yawa da ke nuna cewa SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, da SARS-CoV-2 sun samo asali ne daga bat da kuma yaduwa ga mutane ta hanyar mai watsa shiri.
Ganin cewa kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV ta samo asali ne daga hulɗa tsakanin mutane da foxes a cikin kasuwar ruwa, yana iya zama rufe kasuwar ruwa da kashe duk foxes a ciki wanda ya kawo ƙarshen barkewar cutar SARS.
A irin wannan dalili, ya kamata a cire tururuwa daga kasuwannin da ke da ruwa don hana yaduwar kwayar cutar, saboda gano wasu layukan beta-CoV na tururuwa da ke da kusanci da SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da haka, gaskiyar da kuma hanyar da SARS-CoV-2 ke yaduwa ga mutane ta hanyar tsuntsaye da sauran dabbobi masu shayarwa har yanzu suna buƙatar bayyanawa a cikin binciken gaba.
A gefe guda, MERS-CoV ya daɗe yana cikin raƙuman Arabiya.
Ta zama hanya mai muhimmanci na sufuri da kuma tushen nama, madara, fata, da kuma kayan ɗamara ga mutanen yankin.
An rarraba raƙuman Arabiya a dukan Gabas ta Tsakiya da Afirka.
Saboda haka, ba zai yiwu mu kashe dukkan raƙuma ba don mu iya shawo kan cutar MERS, kamar yadda ake yi a kasuwar namun daji a China don hana yaduwar SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2.
Don dakatar da barkewar cutar MERS, dole ne a yi cikakkiyar hanya don samar da allurar rigakafin raƙuma da ke da tasiri akan MERS-CoV kuma a haɗa ta da sauran matakan sarrafa kamuwa da cuta.
Kafin mu kawar da wannan kwayar cutar, za a iya samun sabon nau'in kwayoyin halitta da zai iya haifar da annoba.
Akwai nau'o'in kwayar cutar da ke yaduwa a cikin daji.
Musamman ma, ƙwayoyin cuta na bat da ke da yiwuwar zama dabbobi sun bambanta sosai.
Akwai yiwuwar cewa wannan kwayar cutar ta zoonotic za ta iya juyawa kuma ta sake haɗuwa, wanda hakan zai haifar da fitowar sabbin kwayar cutar da za ta iya yaduwa da kuma/ko kuma ta yi kisa ga mutane a nan gaba.
Dole ne a daina cin naman daji a wasu wurare a kasar Sin domin rage hulda da dabbobi.
Tare da mummunan kwarewar SARS, MERS, da COVID-19, ya kamata a yi shiri da kuma inganta tsarin magance su.
A gaskiya, ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa sun kasance a duniyar nan tun zamanin dā.
Waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta suna cikin ɗakunan ajiya na halitta har sai an sami damar yaduwa.
Ko da yake batutuwan suna da halaye da yawa da ke taimakawa wajen yaduwar kwayar cutar, za a iya rage damar da mutane ke da shi na hulɗa da batutuwan da sauran namun daji idan aka umurci mutane su guje wa namun daji.
Ana bukatar ci gaba da sa ido kan dabbobi masu shayarwa don fahimtar yanayin CoV da mahaifarsa, wanda zai zama da amfani wajen hana yaduwar dabbobi zuwa ga mutane da kuma barkewar cutar nan gaba.
A ƙarshe, hanya mafi inganci don hana cutar ta kwayar cuta ita ce mutane su nisanta kansu daga mahalli na halitta na kwayar cutar ta kwayar cuta.
Ba a gano wasu ɓangarorin jigon asalin SARS-CoV-2 ba.
Na farko, idan batutuwan sun watsa kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ga tsuntsaye, yanayin da batutuwan da tsuntsaye ke raba yanayin muhalli yana da mahimmanci a sani.
Na biyu, idan batutuwan suna da rawar kai tsaye a watsawa ga mutane, dole ne a ƙayyade yadda mutane ke hulɗa da batutuwan.
Na uku, idan akwai wani dabba mai shayarwa na uku da yake aiki a matsayin mai watsa shiri na ainihi, ya kamata a bayyana yadda dabba mai shayarwa take hulɗa da sauran nau'in, waɗanda suka haɗa da mutane, bat da tsuntsaye.
A ƙarshe, saboda yawancin dabbobi masu shayarwa, ciki har da dabbobin gida, na iya zama masu saukin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2, dole ne a yi gwaji da kuma sa ido kan kamuwa da cutar.
Ko dai a cikin bat, tsuntsaye, ko wasu dabbobi masu shayarwa, ana sa ran cewa SARS-CoV-2 ko kuma kusan kwayar cutar da ta kama za a iya gano ta a cikin mahaifarta na halitta a nan gaba.
Ci gaba da bincike a cikin wannan fannin zai bayyana hanyar juyin halitta na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dabbobi, tare da mahimman abubuwan da ke tattare da rigakafi da sarrafa COVID-19 a cikin mutane.
Ana bukatar sabunta ka'idojin ganewar asali na COVID-19 da kuma wanda aka tabbatar da cutar.
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta buga jagorar gaggawa don ganewar asali da kuma kula da sabon kamuwa da kwayar cutar coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV). Wannan jagorar ya dogara ne akan kwarewarmu kuma ya zama kyakkyawan tunani don yaƙar cutar a duk duniya.
Duk da haka, cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwar cuta ce, kuma iliminmu da wayewarmu suna ƙaruwa bisa binciken bincike da ake yi da kuma kwarewar asibiti; saboda haka, ana ci gaba da sabunta hanyoyin ganewar asali da kulawar.
A cikin wannan wasika, mun amsa ɗaya daga cikin maganganun da ke cikin jagorarmu kuma mun samar da sabbin ka'idojin ganewar asali don al'amarin da aka zata da al'amarin da aka tabbatar bisa ga Jagoran Ganowa da Kulawa don COVID-19 (na bakwai) wanda Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ta bayar.
A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da barkewar cutar, wanda a halin yanzu ana kiransa da sunan cutar coronavirus na 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an sanya wa kwayar cutar sunan coronavirus na 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, WHO ta bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Don yaƙi da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta samar da jagorar gaggawa kuma an buga ta ta yanar gizo a cikin Military Medical Research a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
An yi amfani da wannan littafin tun da aka wallafa shi.
Duk da haka, ya kamata a lura cewa COVID-19 sabuwar cuta ce, kuma iliminmu da wayewarmu suna ƙaruwa bisa binciken bincike da ake yi da kuma kwarewar asibiti; saboda haka, ana ci gaba da sabunta hanyoyin ganewar asali da kulawar.
Misali, Jagorar Ganowa da Kulawa don COVID-19 wanda Hukumar Lafiya ta Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ta fitar (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), tsakanin 16 ga Janairu 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris 2020, hukumar ta fitar da editoci bakwai tare da wasu mahallin da aka canza sosai.
Jagoranmu ya karɓi bayani daga Zhou et al., sun gabatar da shawarwari masu sauƙi na ƙididdigar bisa ga kwarewarsu ta asibiti.
Sakamakon binciken ya ba da sabon bayani game da cutar kuma ya zama muhimmiyar ma'ana ga duniya.
Muna goyon bayan aikin da suka yi kuma muna godiya.
Duk da haka, sakamakon aikin su ya bukaci sabuntawa bisa ga sabon Jagorar Ganowa da Kulawa don COVID-19 (na bakwai na gwaji) da kuma sabon binciken.
Dangane da fitowar ta bakwai (3 Maris 2020), don tabbatar da yanayin da ake tsammani ana buƙatar haɗuwa da ɗayan tarihin tarihin cutar tare da bayyanannun bayyanannun asibiti guda biyu don yin cikakken bincike, ko kuma ana buƙatar cika bayyanannun bayyanannun asibiti guda uku idan babu bayyananniyar tarihin cutar:
Tarihin cutar: (1) tarihin tafiya ko zama a birnin Wuhan da ke kewaye, ko kuma wasu al'ummomin da aka samu rahoton cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (2) tarihin hulɗa da wani mutum da ya kamu da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (tare da gwajin nucleic acid mai kyau); (3) tarihin hulɗa da wani mai zazzabi ko kuma wanda ke fama da cututtukan numfashi daga birnin Wuhan da ke kewaye, ko kuma wasu al'ummomin da aka samu rahoton cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtukan; (4) tarihin hulɗa da wani rukunin mutane da aka tabbatar da cutar (≥ 2 da suka kamu da zazzabi da/ko kuma cututtukan numfashi da suka faru cikin makonni 2 a wani karamin yanki, kamar gida, ofis, aji, da sauransu).
Bayyanar asibiti: (1) zazzabi da/ko alamun numfashi; (2) fasalin hoto na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19; (3) jimlar adadin ƙwayoyin jini na nuna ƙimar ƙwayoyin lymphocyte na al'ada, raguwa, ko raguwa a farkon matakin kamuwa da cuta.
Ganowar tabbatar da cutar ya kamata ya dogara da yanayin da ake tsammani tare da ɗayan waɗannan pathogenic ko hujjojin serological kamar haka: (1) gwajin PCR na ainihi mai kyau don SARS-CoV-2; (2) jerin dukkanin kwayoyin cutar sun nuna babban daidaituwa ga sabon coronavirus da aka sani; (3) tabbatacce ga takamaiman IgM antibody da IgG antibody ga SARS-CoV-2 a cikin gwajin jini; ko kuma canzawar takamaiman IgG na SARS-CoV-2 daga tabbatacce zuwa mara kyau, ko titer ya ƙaru da ≥4 sau biyu a lokacin farfadowa sama da matakin a lokacin gaggawa.
Za mu iya ganin cewa an ƙara gwajin PCR na ainihin lokacin nucleic acid a cikin samfurin numfashi ko jini a cikin na biyu (Janairu 18, 2020) da na uku (Janairu 22, 2020).
An ƙara gano kwayar cuta a cikin samfurin jini a cikin fitowar ta huɗu (Janairu 27, 2020) da ta biyar (Fabrairu 8, 2020); sannan, an ƙara hujja ta serological a fitowar ta bakwai.
Wannan gyare-gyare ya dogara ne akan ci gaba da bincike na masu bincike don neman mafi kyawun kayan aikin gano nucleic acid don saurin ganewar asali, da kuma samfurori daga hanyoyin numfashi ciki har da ɗaukar jini, wanda ke haɓaka wadatar samfuran daban-daban, kuma yana tallafawa shigar da tabbataccen sakamakon antibody a cikin ka'idojin da aka tabbatar.
Bugu da ƙari, akwai ƙarin tabbaci da ke tunasar da mu mu mai da hankali ga marasa lafiya da ba su da alamun bayyanar cututtuka.
Saboda haka, ya kamata a sabunta jadawalin Zhou et al. domin sun rarraba mutanen da ba su da alamun asibiti a matsayin masu "ƙarancin haɗari".
Tsarin ƙididdigar kuma yana buƙatar tabbatarwa a cikin aiki da nazarin asibiti na gaba.
A ƙarshe, muna fatan ƙarin tabbaci zai bayyana kuma mu nemi masu karatu su yi sharhi.
Don ganewar cutar da kuma tabbatar da cutar, muna ba da shawarar bin kuma bin sabon jagora a cikin ƙasarsu.
Ƙungiyarmu za ta kuma riƙa sabunta jagororinmu a kai a kai don taimaka mana.
