Wannan shi ne adadin mutane da suka mutu a rana guda sakamakon cutar.
Har zuwa jiya, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka, Cututtuka da Bincike (IEDCR) ta Bangladesh ta ba da rahoton adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar da suka hada da masu aiki 114 da masu warkewa 33 da ke zaune a gida.
An samu mutuwar mutane 17.
A wani rahoto da aka fitar a shafin yanar gizo, daraktan IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, ta ce mutuwar ta hada da maza hudu da mace daya.
A cewar Dr Meerjady, mutum biyu sun haura shekara 60, biyu sun haura shekara 51 zuwa 60, kuma mutum ɗaya ya haura shekara 41 zuwa 50.
Ya kuma ce biyu daga cikin wadanda suka mutu daga birnin Dhaka ne.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Wani jami'in asibiti ya shaida wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Anadolu Agency cewa daya daga cikin wadanda suka mutu shi ne Jalal Saifur Rahman, daraktan hukumar yaki da cin hanci da rashawa ta Bengal, wanda ke kwance a asibitin Kuwait Maitree.
A ranar Asabar, a cikin sanarwar bidiyo ta yanar gizo, Ministan Sufuri da Tituna Obaidul Quader ya ce za a dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a na tsawon lokaci fiye da yadda aka tsara, har zuwa ranar Asabar mai zuwa.
An fara dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a tun daga ranar 26 ga watan Maris kuma an shirya za ta kare a ranar Asabar, 4 ga watan Afrilu.
Ana ci gaba da ba da izinin jigilar kayayyakin rayuwa - magani, man fetur, da abinci.
An fara samun cutar COVID-19 a Bangladesh a ranar 8 ga Maris, a cikin mutane biyu da suka dawo daga Italiya da kuma matar daya daga cikinsu.
A ranar 19 ga Maris, an warkar da dukan mutanen uku.
Cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta zarce miliyan daya a duniya
A ranar Alhamis, jimillar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar korona SARS-CoV-2 ya zarce miliyan daya a duniya, a cewar bayanan Jami'ar Johns Hopkins.
Akalla 52 000 na mutuwar da aka danganta da COVID-19, cutar da coronavirus ke haifarwa.
Wannan ya faru ne a ranar da Malawi ta tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar korona ta farko da Zambia ta samu mutuwar ta farko da ta shafi cutar korona.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi ikirarin, a ranar Alhamis, cewa ita ce daya daga cikin 'yan kasashen da suka kasance ba su da kamuwa da cutar korona.
Har zuwa jiya, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da rahoton 1,051,635 da aka tabbatar da su, ciki har da 79,332 a cikin awanni ashirin da huɗu tun daga karfe 10 na safe (0800 UTC) a ranar 4 ga Afrilu.
A Amurka, an samu fiye da mutane 244,000 da suka kamu da cutar korona, wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 5,900.
Kamfanin CBS News ya ruwaito, yana ambaton bayanan Jami'ar Johns Hopkins, cewa akwai sama da mutane 1,000 da suka mutu a Amurka sakamakon kamuwa da cutar korona.
A dukan duniya, ƙasashe suna sanar da ƙarin matakai don hana yaduwar cutar.
A ranar Alhamis, Sergei Sobyanin, magajin garin Moscow, ya tsawaita dokar hana fita har zuwa ranar 1 ga watan Mayu.
A kasa baki daya, Shugaba Vladimir Putin ya bayyana cewa, 'yan kasar Rasha za su ci gaba da samun albashi ba tare da sun je aiki ba har zuwa ranar 30 ga watan Afrilu.
Majalisar Portugal ta yi zabe don tsawaita dokar ta baci na tsawon kwanaki 15; zaben ya wuce da kuri'u 215 a kan wannan, goma suka yi kaura, kuma daya ya ki.
Saudiyya ta tsawaita dokar hana fita daga birnin Makka da Madina har tsawon yini; a baya, dokar ta kasance tsakanin karfe uku na yamma zuwa shida na safe.
Thailand na shirin saka dokar hana fita tsakanin karfe 10 na dare zuwa karfe 4 na safe.
Gwamnan Ohio, Mike DeWine, ya sanar da cewa jihar ta tsawaita dokar hana fita har zuwa ranar 1 ga watan Mayu.
