Domain.com, wani shafin sayar da kayayyaki, ya ruwaito cewa wasu masu sayar da kayayyaki sun ba da kayan wanka kyauta ga masu fara yin gwanjo a Melbourne, yayin da aka yi karancin gwanjo saboda masu sayen suna hutu don doguwar hutun ranar Labor Day.
Mujallar ranar Alhamis na NT News, wata jarida da ake bugawa a Darwin, ta ƙunshi shafuffuka takwas na abin sakawa da aka yi niyyar yankewa kuma a yi amfani da su a matsayin kayan wanka.
Shaguna sun yi jinkirin aiwatar da takunkumi, kamar yadda ABC Australia ta ruwaito a ranar 3 ga Maris, suna cewa ba su da shirin aiwatar da takunkumin sayayya.
Russell Zimmerman ya ƙara da cewa wasu kayayyaki ma suna cikin babban bukata, sun haɗa da abin rufe fuska, kayan shafawa, abinci mai bushewa, sabulu, da kuma gari.
