Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana annobar COVID-19 mai gudana - cutar da coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa - a matsayin annoba.
Ko da yake kalmar "annoba" tana nufin yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda cutar take da hatsari ba, WHO ta lura da bukatar karfafawa gwamnatoci gwiwa su dauki mataki:
Dukkanin kasashe na iya canza yanayin cutar.
Idan gwamnati ta gano, gwada, magance, ware, da kuma tura mutanenta a mayar da martani, in ji Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Darakta Janar na WHO.
Muna cikin damuwa sosai saboda yawan yaduwar cutar da kuma tsananin ta da kuma jinkirin da ake yi.
Wani tsohon darektan Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka a Amirka, Dr. Tom Frieden ya ce wannan annoba "ba ta taɓa faruwa ba".
Ya ce a cikin wani rahoto da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu, "ban da mura, babu wata kwayar cuta ta numfashi da aka taɓa lura da ita tun daga lokacin da ta soma ya zuwa lokacin da ta ci gaba da yaɗuwa a dukan duniya".
Ghebreyesus ya bayyana irin wannan ra'ayi, yana cewa "ba mu taɓa ganin annobar da coronavirus ta haifar ba".
Ya ci gaba, "kuma ba mu taɓa ganin wata annoba da za a iya sarrafawa a lokaci ɗaya ba".
Sabon matsayin annobar ya biyo bayan shawarar da WHO ta yanke a watan Janairu wanda ya ayyana annobar a matsayin gaggawa ta kiwon lafiyar jama'a da ke damun duniya.
