Cutar ta haifar da mummunan rikice-rikicen zamantakewar tattalin arziki na duniya, jinkiri ko soke ayyukan al'adu, siyasa, addini, wasanni, da kuma yawan karancin kayayyaki da aka kara da sayayya.
An rufe makarantu da jami'o'i a ƙasashe 193 da kuma a yankuna, wanda ya shafi kashi 99.4 cikin ɗari na ɗaliban duniya.
Rashin gaskiya game da cutar ya bazu a yanar gizo kuma akwai wasu abubuwan da ke nuna kyamar kasashen waje da nuna wariya ga mutanen China, mutanen da ke da asalin Asiya ta Gabas ta Tsakiya da kuma bayyanarsu, da kuma mutanen da suka fito daga yankunan da ke da manyan shari'o'in cutar.
Saboda rage tafiye-tafiye da kuma rufe manyan masana'antu, gurɓataccen iska da fitowar iskar carbon sun ragu.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya a Wuhan, China (babban birnin lardin Hubei), sun ba da rahoton cluster na cutar huhu da ba a san dalilin ba a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 kuma an gudanar da bincike a farkon Janairu, 2020.
Yawancin waɗannan lamuran sun danganci Kasuwar Kasuwancin Kayan Kifin Kayan Kifin na Huanan kuma saboda haka ana zargin cewa kwayar cutar ta zoonotic ne.
Kwayar cutar da ke haifar da annobar an kira ta SARS-CoV-2, sabuwar kwayar cutar da aka gano kuma tana da alaƙa da coronavirus bat, coronavirus na tengger, da SARS-CoV. Mutumin farko da ke da alamun da aka sani ya kamu da cutar a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma mutumin ba shi da alaƙa da alamun da aka ambata a baya.
Daga cikin rukunin farko na masu cutar da aka ruwaito a watan Disamba na 2019, kashi biyu bisa uku sun kasance suna da alaƙa da wannan kasuwa.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020, wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba daga South China Morning Post ya yi hasashen cewa wani shari'ar da za a iya ganowa zuwa 17 ga Nuwamba, 2019, a cikin wani mutum mai shekaru 55 daga lardin Hubei, mai yiwuwa shine na farko. A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020, WHO ta ba da rahoton cewa, tare da sabbin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito sun ragu a China, amma ba zato ba tsammani sun karu a Italiya, Iran, da Koriya ta Kudu, sabon adadin shari'o'in da ke wajen China ya zarce sabon adadin shari'o'in da ke cikin China a karon farko.
Wataƙila akwai ƙaruwar adadin waɗanda ba a ba da rahoton su ba, musamman ma a tsakanin mutanen da ke da ƙananan alamu.
Har zuwa 26 ga Fabrairu, ƙananan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar sun kasance a cikin matasa, tare da mutanen da shekarunsu ba su kai 19 ba suna da kashi 2.4% na masu kamuwa da cutar a duniya. Babban mai ba da shawara kan ilimin kimiyya na Burtaniya, Patrick Vallance, ya kiyasta cewa kashi 60% na yawan mutanen Burtaniya suna buƙatar kamuwa da cutar kafin a sami rigakafin rukuni.
Lamarin ya shafi adadin mutanen da suka yi gwajin COVID-19 kuma sakamakon gwajin ya tabbatar da tabbatacce bisa ga ka'idojin hukuma.
Har zuwa 23 ga watan Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta gwada fiye da kashi 3 cikin ɗari na yawan jama'arta, kuma ƙasashe da yawa sun kafa ƙa'idodin hukuma na ƙin gwada mutane da ke da ƙananan alamun cutar, kamar Italiya, Netherlands, Spain, da Switzerland.
Wani bincike da aka buga a ranar 16 ga watan Maris ya gano cewa a kasar Sin, har zuwa ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an kiyasta cewa kashi 86% na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ba a gano su ba, kuma cewa wannan kamuwa da cutar da ba a rubuta ba ce ta haifar da kashi 79% na kamuwa da cutar.
Wani bincike na kididdiga da aka buga a ranar 30 ga Maris ya kiyasta cewa adadin kamuwa da cutar a Italiya ya fi adadin da aka ruwaito.
