Makarantu a yankin Seattle sun soke karatu a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma a tsakiyar watan Maris, makarantu a duk faɗin ƙasar sun rufe. A ranar 6 ga Maris, 2020, an sanar da Amurka game da hasashen tasirin sabon coronavirus a cikin ƙasar ta hanyar ƙungiyar masana cututtukan cututtuka a Imperial College London.
A wannan ranar, Shugaba Trump ya sanya hannu kan Dokar Shirye-shiryen Coronavirus da Amsa ta Ƙarin Kuɗi, wanda ke ba da tallafin gaggawa na dala biliyan 8.3 ga hukumomin tarayya don amsa annobar.
