An soke wasanni da kuma lokutan wasanni. A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Trump ya sanar da hana tafiye-tafiye ga yawancin kasashen Turai, sai dai Birtaniya, na tsawon kwanaki 30, wanda ya fara aiki a ranar 13 ga watan Maris.
