A ranar 25 ga Maris, gwamnan New York ya ce an yi nasarar aiwatar da takunkumin hana yaduwar jama'a saboda ƙididdigar ƙaruwar masu kamuwa da cutar ta ragu daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa kwanaki 4.7.
A ranar 28 ga watan Maris, an sami mutane 32,308 da suka kamu da cutar a birnin New York City, kuma mutane 672 ne suka mutu sakamakon cutar. A ranar 26 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta samu karin wadanda suka kamu da cutar fiye da kowace kasa a duniya, ciki har da China da Italiya.
A cewar rahotanni na kafofin watsa labarai a ranar 30 ga watan Maris, Shugaba Trump na Amurka ya yanke shawarar tsawaita ka'idojin hana mutane shiga kasashen waje har zuwa ranar 30 ga watan Afrilu.
A wannan rana, jirgin asibiti mai suna USNS Comfort, mai gado 1,000, ya sauka a New York.
