A jihar New York, an zargi fadar White House da yin watsi da barazanar da kuma sarrafa sakonnin ta hanyar umarci jami'an kiwon lafiya da masana kimiyya da su daidaita maganganun jama'a da wallafe-wallafen da suka shafi kwayar cutar a ofishin Mataimakin Shugaban kasa Mike Pence.
Gabaɗaya, amincewa da yadda Trump ya gudanar da rikicin ya rabu tsakanin bangarorin.
