An yi amfani da nazarin yanayin tafiyar jirgin sama don tsarawa da kuma hango hasashen yanayin yaduwar cutar kuma an buga shi a cikin The Journal of Travel Medicine a tsakiyar Janairu 2020.
Bisa ga bayanan 2018 daga Kungiyar Sufurin Jiragen Sama ta Duniya, mutane da suka fi tafiya daga Wuhan sun kasance a Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, da Taipei.
Dubai, Sydney, da Melbourne kuma an bayar da rahoton cewa su ne wuraren da mutane ke zuwa daga Wuhan.
