Hukumomin Australia sun kwashe 'yan kasar su 277 a ranar 3 da 4 ga watan Fabrairu zuwa Cibiyar Kula da Yanayin Tsibirin Kirsimeti, wadda aka mayar da ita cibiyar killace mutane, inda suka zauna na tsawon kwanaki 14.
