An yi gwajin lafiya kafin tashi kuma an bar wasu 'yan Afirka ta Kudu huɗu da ke nuna alamun cutar coronavirus don rage haɗarin.
Sai dai mutanen Afirka ta Kudu da suka yi gwajin rashin lafiya ne kawai aka mayar da su gida.
Bisa ga sakamakon gwajin, an ba da izini ga duk waɗannan 'yan Afirka ta Kudu, gami da ma'aikatan jirgin, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal,' yan sanda, da sojoji da ke cikin ayyukan jin kai; a matsayin abin da ya kamata, duk sun kasance a karkashin kulawa da keɓewa na kwanaki 14 a The Ranch Resort.
A ranar 20 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta fara janye wasu dakarunta daga Iraki saboda annobar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa kasashe 21 (da suka hada da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar, da Iran) sun aika da agaji zuwa kasar Sin.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin a jami'o'in Amurka da dama sun hada kai don tura agaji zuwa yankunan kasar Sin da cutar ta shafa, tare da wasu kungiyoyi da suka hada kai daga yankin Chicago; an bayar da rahoton cewa sun samu nasarar tura kayan rufe fuska 50,000 na N95 zuwa asibitoci a lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu. Kungiyar agaji ta Direct Relief, a hade tare da FedEx, ta tura kayan rufe fuska 200,000 da sauran kayan kariya, ciki har da safofin hannu da riguna, ta hanyar jigilar iska ta gaggawa zuwa asibitin Wuhan Union a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don tallafawa binciken allurar rigakafi da ƙoƙarin magance ta, da kuma kare "mutane masu haɗari a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya".
Interaktion ta ruwaito cewa gwamnatin China ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, bayan Sanata Richard Gordon ya aika da abin rufe fuska miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta tura dala miliyan 2.26 zuwa kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska miliyan ɗaya zuwa Wuhan, Turkiyya ta aika da kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika da tan 13 na kayan aikin likita zuwa Wuhan, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da gudummawar safofin hannu na likita miliyan 18 zuwa China, Jamus ta ba da gudummawar kayan aikin likita da suka hada da rigunan Hazmat 10,000, kuma Amurka ta ba da gudummawar tan 17.8 na kayan aikin likita zuwa China tare da alƙawarin ƙarin dala miliyan 100 a cikin tallafin kuɗi ga ƙasashen da abin ya shafa. Bayan da lamuran da ke cikin China suka daidaita, Amurka ta aika da taimako ga ƙasashen da cutar ta shafa.
A watan Maris, Sin, Cuba, da Rasha sun aika da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya da masana don taimakawa Italiya magance annobar coronavirus.
Kamfanin Jack Ma ya aika da kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1, da abin rufe fuska miliyan 6, da kuma riguna na kariya dubu 60 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha, domin kungiyar tarayyar Afirka ta rarraba su.
Daga baya, ya aika da kayan gwaji 5,000, da abin rufe fuska 100,000, da kuma na'urorin numfashi biyar zuwa Panama.
Ma ya kuma ba da gudummawar kayayyakin kiwon lafiya ga Kanada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia, da Jamhuriyar Czech sun nuna damuwa game da ingancin abin rufe fuska da kayan gwajin da aka yi a kasar Sin.
Misali, Spain ta janye kayan gwajin coronavirus 58,000 da aka yi da kasar Sin da suka yi daidai da kashi 30%; yayin da Netherlands ta janye 600,000 na kayan rufe fuska na kasar Sin da suka lalace.
Belgium ta kuma kwashe masks 100,000 da ba za a iya amfani da su ba, da ake zargin sun fito ne daga China, amma a zahiri daga Colombia.
A wani bangare kuma, tallafin da kasar Sin ta bayar ya samu karbuwa a wasu sassan Latin Amurka da Afirka. A ranar 2 ga watan Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya kaddamar da wani gaggawa na tallafi ga kasashe masu tasowa.
Hukumar ta WHO ta yaba wa gwamnatin kasar Sin kan kokarin da take yi na sarrafawa da kuma shawo kan annobar.
WHO ta lura da bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS ta 2002-2004 lokacin da aka zargi hukumomin China da yin rufin asiri don haka suka hana rigakafin da kuma hanawa da kuma rikicin yanzu tare da gwamnatin tsakiya "ta ba da sabuntawa na yau da kullun don kauce wa tashin hankali a lokacin hutun Sabuwar Shekarar Lunar.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a mayar da martani ga matakin gwamnatin tsakiya na sanya takunkumin hana zirga-zirga a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya ce duk da cewa matakin "a bayyane yake ba shawarar WHO ba ne", amma kuma "wani muhimmin alama ne na jajircewar da ake da ita na dakile barkewar cutar a inda cutar ta fi yawa" kuma ya kira shi "marasa misali a tarihin kiwon lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, bayan tabbatar da yaduwar cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum a wajen China da kuma karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a wasu kasashe, WHO ta ayyana annobar a matsayin gaggawa ta gaggawa ta Duniya (PHEIC), wato PHEIC ta shida tun lokacin da aka fara aiwatar da annobar cutar cutar alade a shekarar 2009.
Darakta Janar na WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce an bayyana PHEIC ne domin "hadarin yaduwar duniya, musamman ga ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi da matsakaitan kuɗi waɗanda ba su da tsarin kiwon lafiya mai kyau.
Da yake amsawa game da aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya bayyana cewa "babu wani dalili da zai sa a aiwatar da matakan da ke kawo cikas ga tafiye-tafiye da cinikayya ta duniya ba tare da bukatarsu ba" kuma "WHO ba ta ba da shawarar hana cinikayya da motsi ba".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya da su ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 da za a yi amfani da su wajen samar da kudade don shirya a kasashe masu karancin kudin shiga, tana mai ambaton gaggawa don tallafa wa kasashen da "ba su da tsarin gano mutanen da suka kamu da cutar idan annobar ta barke".
Tedros ya kara da cewa "iyakar ƙarfinmu yana kan mafi raunin sarkar" kuma ya bukaci al'ummar duniya da su "saka hannun jari a yanzu ko kuma su biya ƙarin a nan gaba". A taron manema labarai na ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta sanya COVID-19 a matsayin sunan cutar ga wannan kwayar.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya bayyana cewa Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince ya ba da "amsa ta hanyar rarraba dukkan iko na tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya".
Bayan haka, Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kunna Kungiyar Gudanar da Rikicin don ba da damar daidaita duk amsar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda WHO ta ce zai ba su damar "mai da hankali kan maganin kiwon lafiya, yayin da sauran hukumomi za su iya amfani da ƙwarewarsu don magance tasirin annobar a fannonin zamantakewa, tattalin arziki, da ci gaba. "
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, an kunna wani Kungiyar Haɗin gwiwa ta China da WHO ke jagoranta; wannan tawagar tana da nufin samar da ƙwararrun ƙwararrun ƙasashen duniya da na WHO a China don taimakawa gudanarwar cikin gida da kimanta "taurin tsananin cutar da yaduwar cutar" ta hanyar gudanar da bita da tarurrukan tare da hukumomin matakin ƙasa da kuma yin ziyarar filin don kimanta "tasirin ayyukan magance su a matakin lardi da gunduma, wanda ya haɗa da birane da karkara".A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta bayyana cewa "duniya dole ne ta yi ƙarin shiri don fuskantar yiwuwar cutar ta coronavirus" kuma ta ce, kodayake yana da wuri a kira ta a matsayin annoba, ƙasashe dole ne su kasance cikin "tsarin shiri".
A cikin martani ga barkewar cutar a Iran, WHO ta aika da Kungiyar Haɗin gwiwa zuwa can don kimanta halin da ake ciki. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce za a ɗaga darajar barazanar coronavirus a duniya daga "babba" zuwa "mai matukar girma", wannan shine matakin tsaro da kimanta haɗarin mafi girma.
A wata sanarwa, Mike Ryan, babban darektan shirin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya na WHO, ya yi gargadin cewa, "Lokaci ya yi da kowace gwamnati a duniya za ta fuskanci gaskiya: Ku kasance a faɗake.
Wannan cuta na iya zuwa wurinku kuma dole ne ku kasance a shirye", kuma ya nace cewa matakan da suka dace na magance ta na iya taimakawa duniya ta guji "mafi munin".
Ryan ya ci gaba da cewa, bayanan na yanzu ba su ba da damar jami'an kiwon lafiya su ayyana annobar duniya ba, ya ce irin wannan sanarwar na nufin "ainihin mun yarda cewa kowane mutum a duniya zai kamu da cutar".
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, WHO ta ayyana annobar coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
Darakta Janar na WHO ya ce WHO "ta damu matuka game da yawan yaduwar cutar da kuma tsananin cutar, da kuma jinkirin da ake yi wajen magance ta". WHO ta sha suka saboda rashin kulawar da ta yi wajen magance cutar, wanda ya hada da jinkirin ayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya da kuma rarraba cutar a matsayin annoba.
Daya daga cikin mummunan martani ya hada da takardar neman izini da mutane 733,000 suka sanya hannu a ranar 6 ga Afrilu, wanda aka aika wa Darakta Janar na WHO Tedros Adhanom don neman ya yi murabus.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, dubun-dubatar masana harkokin kare hakkin dan adam na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sun jaddada girmama hakkin kowane mutum yayin annobar COVID-19.
Ƙungiyar ta ce kowa yana da hakkin ya yi aikin ceton rai kuma gwamnati ce ke da alhakin yin hakan.
Ƙungiyar ta jaddada cewa rashin albarkatu ko inshorar lafiya ba za a yi amfani da su ba don yin wariya ga wasu rukuni.
Masana sun nanata cewa kowa yana da hakkin samun lafiya, har da nakasassu, 'yan tsiraru, tsofaffi, 'yan gudun hijira, marasa gida, matalauta, fursunoni, 'yan gudun hijira, da sauran kungiyoyin da ke bukatar tallafin gwamnati.
Kungiyoyin gwamnatoci na duniya suna kokarin magance tasirin zamantakewa da tattalin arziki na rikicin COVID-19.
Kungiyar hadin gwiwar tattalin arziki da ci gaba ta kaddamar da wani shiri na samar da cikakken bayani kan yadda ake gudanar da manufofin a kasashe a duniya, da kuma ra'ayoyi da shawarwari.
Daga manufofi don ƙarfafa tsarin kiwon lafiya da tattalin arziƙin duniya zuwa magance tasirin keɓaɓɓun keɓaɓɓu da ƙuntatawa na tafiye-tafiye, cibiyoyin dijital sun haɗa da Mai bin diddigin Manufofin Jiha, kuma suna da nufin taimaka wa ƙasashe su koya daga juna da kuma sauƙaƙe haɗin kai na duniya don magance ƙalubalen coronavirus.
Gwamnatin China ta fuskanci suka daga Amurka, Ministan Ofishin Ministan Burtaniya Michael Gove, da kuma dan Shugaban Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, kan yadda suka magance annobar da ta bulla a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
An sallami wasu jami'an gudanarwa na jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin (CPC) dangane da yadda suka gudanar da aikin killacewa a yankin tsakiyar kasar, wanda ke nuna rashin gamsuwa da yadda hukumomin siyasa suka mayar da martani kan annobar a yankin.
Wasu masu sharhi sun yi imanin cewa an yi wannan matakin ne don kare babban sakataren jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin Xi Jinping daga fushin jama'a game da annobar coronavirus.
Wasu jami'an kasar Sin, kamar Zhao Lijian, sun yi watsi da ikirarin da suka yi a baya game da barkewar cutar coronavirus da ta fara a Wuhan, kuma sun goyi bayan ka'idodin maƙarƙashiya game da COVID-19 da ke fitowa daga Amurka ko Italiya.
Gwamnatin Amurka Donald Trump ta kira coronavirus "virus na kasar Sin" ko "virus na Wuhan" kuma ta ce "aikin da China ke yi na rufe ido ya ba da karfi ga cutar da ta zama annoba ta duniya". Wannan furucin ya yi ta fama da wasu masu sukar nuna wariyar launin fata da kuma "jawo hankali daga gazawar gwamnatinsa wajen magance cutar korona".
Jaridar Daily Beast ta samu wani sakon gwamnatin Amurka wanda ke bayyana dabarun sadarwa kuma a bayyane yake ya fito ne daga kwamitin tsaron kasa, tare da dabarun da aka ambata a matsayin "Dukkanin China.
An gaya mana mu gwada kuma mu isar da wannan sakon ta kowace hanya da za mu iya, ciki har da taron manema labarai da kuma nuna kanmu a talabijin". Kafofin watsa labarai kamar Politico, Foreign Policy, da Bloomberg sun yi ikirarin cewa kokarin da China ke yi na aika da agaji ga kasashen da cutar ta shafa na daga cikin farfagandar da take yi don shafar duniya.
Shugaban harkokin wajen Tarayyar Turai Josep Borrell ya yi gargadin cewa akwai "wani bangare na siyasa, wanda ya ƙunshi yaƙi don samun tasiri ta hanyar jujjuya gaskiya da 'siyasa ta karimci.' "
Borrell ya kuma ce, "Tashin ya na tura saƙo da cewa, ba kamar Amurka ba, su abokan tarayya ne masu alhakin gaskiya".
China ta kuma bukaci Amurka ta dage takunkumin da ta kafa kan Syria da Venezuela da kuma Iran, kuma ta ce ta tura taimakon agaji ga kasashen biyu na karshe.
An dakatar da gudummawar Jack Ma ta kayan masks 100,000 ga Cuba ta takunkumin Amurka a ranar 3 ga Afrilu.
An kuma zargi hukumomin Amurka da tura taimakon da aka yi niyya ga wasu ƙasashe zuwa ƙasarsu.
An kuma samu rigima game da abin rufe fuska tsakanin wasu ƙasashe, kamar Jamus, Austria, da Switzerland; da Jamhuriyar Czech da Italiya.
Ƙari ga haka, Turkiyya ta kwashe ɗarurruwan na'urorin numfashi da aka yi niyyar turawa zuwa ƙasar Spain.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Italiya ta soki rashin hadin kan Tarayyar Turai ga Italiya da cutar coronavirus ta shafa.
Maurizio Massari, jakadan Italiya a Tarayyar Turai, ya ce "Shayana ce kawai ke amsawa a bangaren kasashen biyu.
Hakika, wannan ba kyakkyawan alamar haɗin kai na Turai ba ne".
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, bayan samun kiran waya daga Firayim Ministan Italiya Giuseppe Conte, Shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin ya tura sojojin Rasha don aika da ma'aikatan lafiya na soja, motocin kashe cututtuka na musamman, da sauran kayan aikin likita zuwa Italiya.
Jaridar La Stampa ta Italiya ta yi ƙaulin wani "babban jami'in siyasa" da ba a san sunansa ba da ya ce kashi 80 cikin ɗari na taimakon da Rasha take bayarwa "ba shi da amfani ko kuma ba shi da amfani ga Italiya".
Majiyar ta zargi Rasha da kai harin "na siyasa da kuma na diflomasiyya".
Shugaban Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, da Ministan Harkokin Wajen Italiya Luigi Di Maio sun yi watsi da rahoton kuma sun nuna godiyarsu.
Rasha ta kuma aika da jirgin ruwa mai dauke da kayan kiwon lafiya zuwa Amurka.
