Gwajin dakin gwaje-gwaje na cutar coronavirus na numfashi na 2019 (COVID-19) da kwayar SARS-CoV-2 ya hada da hanyoyin da ke gano kasancewar kwayar cutar da kuma wanda ke gano ƙwayoyin cuta da aka samar a cikin martani ga kamuwa da cuta.
