An kuma gano bayyanar mRNA ACE2 a cikin cerebral cortex, striatum, hypothalamus, da kuma kwakwalwar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine a matsayin mai daidaita ACE.
ACE tana karya hormone angiotensin I zuwa angiotensin II ta hanyar vasokonstriktion.
A ƙarshe, ACE2 ya yanke amino acid phenylalanine na carboxyl na ƙarshe daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma ya hydrolyze shi zuwa angiotensin (1-7) mai fadada jini (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma na iya karya wasu peptides da suka hada da [des-Arg9] -bradikinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita zirga-zirgar membrane na SLC6A19 mai ɗaukar amino acid kuma yana da hannu a cikin cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin na membrane, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban wurin shiga cikin sel don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta, waɗanda suka haɗa da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, ɗaure furotin S1 a kan SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 spikes tare da yankin enzymatic ACE2 a farfajiyar ƙwayoyin cuta yana haifar da endosytosis da kuma sauya kwayar cutar da enzyme zuwa cikin endosomes da ke cikin ƙwayoyin cuta.
Wannan shigarwar kwayar cutar kuma tana buƙatar priming na furotin S ta mai masaukin TMPRSS2, wanda hana shi a halin yanzu ana binciken shi azaman magani mai yuwuwa. Wannan ya haifar da hasashen cewa rage matakan ACE2 a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na iya taimakawa wajen yaƙar kamuwa da cuta.
Duk da haka, yawancin ƙungiyoyi masu sana'a da hukumomi masu tsarawa suna ba da shawarar ci gaba da maganin ACE da kuma ARB na yau da kullum.
Wani nazari da kuma nazarin tsarin, wanda aka buga a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012, ya gano cewa "amfani da masu hana ACE ya haifar da raguwar 34% a cikin haɗarin ciwon huhu idan aka kwatanta da na kula".
Bugu da ƙari, "amfani da masu hana ACE ya kuma rage haɗarin ciwon huhu a cikin marasa lafiya da ke da haɗarin ciwon huhu, musamman marasa lafiya da ke fama da bugun jini da kuma rashin ƙarfi na zuciya.
Amfani da masu hana ACE an kuma danganta shi da rage mutuwar da ke da nasaba da ciwon huhu, ko da yake sakamakon ba shi da ƙarfi idan aka kwatanta da haɗarin ciwon huhu gaba ɗaya".
Ana sa ran ACE2 na mutum mai haɗuwa (rhACE2) ya zama sabon magani don raunin huhu na huhu, kuma ya bayyana don haɓaka haemodynamics na huhu da ƙoshin oxygen a cikin berayen da ke da cutar rashin ƙarfi na lipoplysakaride.
