Koyaya, ba duk tsarin da ke da sabar cibiyar ke buƙatar samun damar bayanan wurin mutum ba; an ƙirƙiri wasu tsarin da ke kare sirrin sirri kuma suna amfani da sabar cibiyar kawai don sadarwa (duba sashe a ƙasa).
