An gwada wannan dabarar a SARS ba tare da sakamako mai kyau ba.
Rashin tasirin kwayar cutar shine tsarin aiki da ake tsammanin maganin rigakafin rigakafin zai iya daidaita kariya akan SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da haka, wasu hanyoyin, kamar su cytotoxicity na kwayoyin halitta da ke dogara da antibody da/ko phagocytosis, ma suna yiwuwa.
Wani nau'i na maganin rigakafin rigakafi, alal misali, yana amfani da rigakafin monoclonal da aka samar, yana ci gaba.
Za a iya inganta samar da maganin warkarwa, wanda shine ruwan da ke cikin jinin mai warkewa wanda ke dauke da takamaiman rigakafi ga kwayar cutar, don saurin amfani.
